<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" version="2.0"><channel><title>RebeccaChambers blog</title><link>https://rebecaachambers.github.io</link><description>The last stubbornness of a technical geek</description><copyright>RebeccaChambers blog</copyright><docs>http://www.rssboard.org/rss-specification</docs><generator>python-feedgen</generator><image><url>https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/191683603?v=4</url><title>avatar</title><link>https://rebecaachambers.github.io</link></image><lastBuildDate>Wed, 13 Aug 2025 16:14:40 +0000</lastBuildDate><managingEditor>RebeccaChambers blog</managingEditor><ttl>60</ttl><webMaster>RebeccaChambers blog</webMaster><item><title>在日本有记录的文献中，1937-1945年中共一共击杀了多少日本军人</title><link>https://rebecaachambers.github.io/post/zai-ri-ben-you-ji-lu-de-wen-xian-zhong-%EF%BC%8C1937-1945-nian-zhong-gong-yi-gong-ji-sha-le-duo-shao-ri-ben-jun-ren.html</link><description>根据日本军方文献（如日本防卫厅防卫研究所战史室编撰的记录），1937-1945年间中共军队（主要为八路军和新四军）在抗日战争中通过游击战和其他作战形式对日军造成的损失可以在若干文献中找到零散数据，但没有一份日本官方文献提供明确的、针对整个抗战期间中共军队击杀日军总数的综合统计。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://rebecaachambers.github.io/post/zai-ri-ben-you-ji-lu-de-wen-xian-zhong-%EF%BC%8C1937-1945-nian-zhong-gong-yi-gong-ji-sha-le-duo-shao-ri-ben-jun-ren.html</guid><pubDate>Fri, 11 Jul 2025 07:16:44 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>华裔不等于中国人：兼论中国历史上朝代对外自称的演变</title><link>https://rebecaachambers.github.io/post/hua-yi-bu-deng-yu-zhong-guo-ren-%EF%BC%9A-jian-lun-zhong-guo-li-shi-shang-zhao-dai-dui-wai-zi-cheng-de-yan-bian.html</link><description>在现代语境中，“华裔”与“中国人”常被混淆，但二者有着本质区别。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://rebecaachambers.github.io/post/hua-yi-bu-deng-yu-zhong-guo-ren-%EF%BC%9A-jian-lun-zhong-guo-li-shi-shang-zhao-dai-dui-wai-zi-cheng-de-yan-bian.html</guid><pubDate>Sun, 06 Jul 2025 06:30:15 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>究竟谁才是真正的中国？中国真的有5000年历史吗？</title><link>https://rebecaachambers.github.io/post/jiu-jing-shui-cai-shi-zhen-zheng-de-zhong-guo-%EF%BC%9F-zhong-guo-zhen-de-you-5000-nian-li-shi-ma-%EF%BC%9F.html</link><description>“中国”一词在古代多指中原地区或中华文化整体，带有地理、文化或政治正统的含义，但作为正式国号或对外自称的情况较少。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://rebecaachambers.github.io/post/jiu-jing-shui-cai-shi-zhen-zheng-de-zhong-guo-%EF%BC%9F-zhong-guo-zhen-de-you-5000-nian-li-shi-ma-%EF%BC%9F.html</guid><pubDate>Sun, 06 Jul 2025 05:45:28 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>